title: Amanda Seales
itunes:title: Amanda Seales
description:
This week on GOOD FOR YOU Whitney and Emily talk about their stalkers and Whitney’s sex scene in the new Foo Fighters movie. Then the incredible comedian/author/actress/musician Amanda Seales (INSECURE) is here and she and Whitney have a conversation about Seales’ work and Whitney gives her tips on how to potty train her dog. Check out SMART FUNNY & BLACK Patreon, SMART FUNNY & BLACK radio show, UNION NEWSLETTER, and Amanda’s podcast SMALL DOSES.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
